<h1 class="text-center mb-5 text-uppercase title-border">
  Какой сервис вы ищите?
</h1>

<div class="form-group mb-4">
  <p class="my-1"><b>Описание услуг</b></p>
  <textarea maxlength="500" class="form-control form-control-lg" id="postServiceDetailsDescription"
    name="postServiceDetailsDescription" rows="5" placeholder="Describe the service you're looking to purchase..."
    onkeyup="textAreaWordCounter(this, 'postServiceDetailsDescriptionTextAreaWordCounter');" required>
<%= jobPost.postServiceDetailsDescription %></textarea>
  <div class="text-end mt-1">
    <span id="postServiceDetailsDescriptionTextAreaWordCounter">
      <%= jobPost.postServiceDetailsDescription ? jobPost.postServiceDetailsDescription.length : 0 %>
    </span>
    <span> / 500</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="custom-file-container" data-upload-id="myUniqueUploadId">
  <label><b>Attach File</b>
    <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="custom-file-container__image-clear" title="Clear Image"></a></label>
  <label class="custom-file-container__custom-file">
    <input type="file" class="custom-file-container__custom-file__custom-file-input" accept="*"
      id="postRequestAttachFiles" name="attachFiles" value="<%= jobPost.attachFiles.originalname %>" required multiple
      aria-label="Choose File" />
    <input type="hidden" name="MAX_FILE_SIZE" value="10485760" />
    <span class="custom-file-container__custom-file__custom-file-control"></span>
  </label>
  <div class="custom-file-container__image-preview" id="attachFilepreview"></div>
</div>

<div class="row mb-4">
  <p class="my-2"><b>Выберите категорию для этой услуги</b></p>
  <div class="form-group col-md-6 mb-3">
    <select class="form-select form-select-lg" id="category" name="category" required>
      <option value="<%= jobPost.category %> " selected>
        <%= jobPost.category ? jobPost.category : 'Select a category' %>
      </option>
    </select>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group col-md-6 mb-3">
    <select class="form-select form-select-lg" id="subCategory" name="subCategory" required>
      <option value="<%= jobPost.subCategory %> " selected>
        <%= jobPost.subCategory ? jobPost.subCategory : 'Select a sub category' %>
      </option>
    </select>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mb-4">
  <p class="my-2">
    <b>После того, как вы разместите свой заказ, когда вы хотите, чтобы ваша услуга была доставлена?</b>
  </p>
  <input type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="How many Days..." name="deliveryDay"
    value="<%= jobPost.deliveryDay  %>" required />
</div>

<div class="mb-4">
  <p class="my-2"><b>Какой у вас бюджет на эту услугу?</b></p>
  <input type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="How much Dollars($)..." name="price"
    value="<%= jobPost.price %>" required />
</div>